page.title: 13Food in 1985,Bitteswell
page.content: This is a list of some third year girls collected that they eat in 1985. Their favourite foods are: MacDonalds hamburgers,barbecues, macaroni cheese,spaghetti,pizza, carrots,broccoli,chicken,cheese, apples,bananas,crisps,potatoes, crisps,potatoes,chocolate,ice-cream, beef,lamb,pork,steak,egg,cucumber, lemon meringue pie,onions,liver, tomatoes,lettuce,sweetcorn,beans and mustard,oranges. Foods they don't like but still eat are: sausages,bacon,fish in cheese sauce,ham,bread,cheese spread,cereals, cauliflower,runner beans,peas,fish and chips,mushrooms and rice. Drinks they like are: lemon, milkshake,fresh fruit juice,Ribena, lemonade and cola.
